</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-51_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-52_ pf-text-1"><strong>Obsessions</strong> - Intense and focused interests in specific subjects, objects, or activities. These can range from common interests like trains or animals to unique topics such as licence plate numbers or vacuum cleaners.
